Bernie's -- no one questions
Bernie's authenticity on those

03:18.131 --> 03:20.000 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
issues.

03:20.000 --> 03:24.471 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Later, the vice
president said that wasn't a
criticism of Clinton. He said

03:24.471 --> 03:29.576 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that, as secretary of state, her
focus had rightly been on
foreign policy.

03:29.576 --> 03:35.182 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There's been new trouble in
Germany over the wave of
migrants pouring into the
country.

03:35.182 --> 03:41.121 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
More than 200 anti-immigration
protesters tore through the city
of Leipzig last night.

03:41.121 --> 03:47.027 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They carried racist signs and
shouted anti-Muslim slogans.
Dozens of police responded to
the

03:47.027 --> 03:53.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
scene and made arrests after
violence erupted. The rioters
smashed windows and vandalized

03:53.166 --> 03:58.738 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
several buildings. Earlier, some
2,000 protesters had marched
peacefully.

03:58.738 --> 04:05.412 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Japan warned today that it will
send armed vessels to keep
China's Navy away from disputed

04:05.412 --> 04:11.284 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
islands. The Senkaku Islands, in
the East China Sea, are claimed
by both nations. A

04:11.284 --> 04:16.723 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
top official in Tokyo says that
Japan means to control the
waters around them.

04:16.723 --> 04:20.827 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
YOSHIHIDE SUGA, Japanese Chief
Cabinet Secretary (through
translator): This objective was
approved

04:20.827 --> 04:26.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
by the cabinet in May last year,
stating that foreign naval
passage into Japanese seas that

04:26.366 --> 04:29.569 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
aren't considered nonthreatening
will trigger seaborne policing
action, and will be dealt

04:29.569 --> 04:32.606 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
with by the self-defense force.

04:32.606 --> 04:37.244 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Meanwhile, the
Philippines' Supreme Court
upheld a security deal with

04:37.244 --> 04:43.083 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the U.S. amid rising tensions in
the South China Sea. Manila
hopes that an increased

04:43.083 --> 04:48.688 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
U.S. military presence will fend
off aggressive Chinese moves
there.

04:48.688 --> 04:54.427 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
