a look back at President Obama's
previous State of the

06:48.608 --> 06:53.446 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Union addresses, plus a look
forward to tonight's speech with
the White House chief of staff;

06:53.446 --> 07:09.796 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ISIS blamed for a deadly blast
