08:12.926 --> 08:15.462 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: That's John
Feehery, GOP strategist and
former spokesman for House

08:15.462 --> 08:17.997 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Speaker Dennis Hastert.

08:17.997 --> 08:23.503 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN FEEHERY: I think the
president is really kind of
finished on the legacy front.
His

08:23.503 --> 08:28.775 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
