day somewhat dramatically,
because he's a lame-duck.

08:28.775 --> 08:30.377 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
STEPHANIE CUTTER, Former Obama
Deputy Campaign Manager: I don't
think he's considering himself

08:30.377 --> 08:33.880 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
