has a lot to get done.

08:33.880 --> 08:36.349 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: And that's
Stephanie Cutter. She's a
Democratic consultant and a
former

08:36.349 --> 08:39.285 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
