08:39.285 --> 08:41.788 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
STEPHANIE CUTTER: There's lots
of talk about this being an
election year, and nothing's

08:41.788 --> 08:47.060 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
