ways to make progress, it's
President Obama.

08:55.668 --> 08:59.773 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: With voters
preoccupied with who will be
next the in the Oval Office, the

08:59.773 --> 09:05.044 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
