his last day in office, or, in a
crisis:

09:19.759 --> 09:22.262 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GEORGE W. BUSH, Former President
of the United States: We're in
the midst of a serious financial

09:22.262 --> 09:26.699 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
crisis, and the federal
government is responding with
decisive action.

09:26.699 --> 09:30.737 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Push major
measures, like the Troubled
Asset Relief Program, known as

09:30.737 --> 09:35.275 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
