sending that repeal to the
president's desk.

10:00.900 --> 10:06.072 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: It is a kind of
last yearlong duel between the
GOP and Democratic president.

10:06.072 --> 10:11.811 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
