like the Dodd-Frank Wall Street
reform bill and climate change.

10:15.682 --> 10:17.951 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Again, Feehery:

10:17.951 --> 10:23.723 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN FEEHERY: He's going to be
pushing for Dodd-Frank
regulations, which is going to

10:23.723 --> 10:30.530 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
