emissions on things like coal.

10:45.378 --> 10:50.450 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Cutter sees
foreign policy as another of
Obama's final year legacy agenda

10:50.450 --> 10:54.687 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
items. She points to Obama's
decision to reestablish ties
with Cuba, including reopening
the U.S.

10:54.687 --> 10:57.056 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
