10:57.056 --> 11:01.694 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STEPHANIE CUTTER: Cuba is a
significant piece of this
president's legacy. I think the
president,

11:01.694 --> 11:05.031 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
