those doors stay open.

11:07.967 --> 11:13.039 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Polls show more
Americans disapprove of Obama's
performance than approve.

11:13.039 --> 11:16.843 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
