11:27.287 --> 11:33.760 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA: If we make some
good choices now, whoever the
next president is, whoever

11:33.760 --> 11:39.899 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
