many as 20, are bringing Muslim
Americans as their guests.

13:50.229 --> 13:54.434 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Now, that's not about President
Obama's agenda. That's clearly
about the 2016 campaign, which

13:54.434 --> 13:57.804 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I think will be woven
through this speech.

13:57.804 --> 14:00.506 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
One last note, Judy. I have
talked to a lot of people about
this speech tonight, but I

14:00.506 --> 14:05.178 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
have to say the most insightful
might have been my Uber driver
on the way here, a man

14:05.178 --> 14:09.749 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
named Earl Wiggins (ph), an
Obama fan, he said. He said he
wants to hear the president

14:09.749 --> 14:12.852 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
